query:
SELECT 
  d.id as deficiency_id, 
  d.assessmentId, 
  d.projectId, 
  d.estimatedCost,
  a.id as assessment_id,
  a.assetId
FROM deficiencies d
LEFT JOIN assessments a ON d.assessmentId = a.id
WHERE d.estimatedCost > 0
LIMIT 10;
